{
  "video_id": "zMWYQRKuc5M",
  "title": "A better way to talk about love | Mandy Len Catron",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 12553.0,
      "end_time": 17237.0,
      "text": "OK, so today I want to talk about how we talk about love."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 17237.0,
      "end_time": 18411.0,
      "text": "And specifically,"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18411.0,
      "end_time": 22673.0,
      "text": "I want to talk about what&#39;s wrong with how we talk about love."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 22673.0,
      "end_time": 26104.0,
      "text": "Most of us will probably fall in love a few times"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 26104.0,
      "end_time": 27593.0,
      "text": "over the course of our lives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 27593.0,
      "end_time": 31827.0,
      "text": "and in the English language, this metaphor, falling,"
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 31827.0,
      "end_time": 35592.0,
      "text": "is really the main way that we talk about that experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 35592.0,
      "end_time": 36767.0,
      "text": "I don&#39;t know about you,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 36767.0,
      "end_time": 38718.0,
      "text": "but when I conceptualize this metaphor,"
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 38718.0,
      "end_time": 42076.0,
      "text": "what I picture is straight out of a cartoon --"
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 42076.0,
      "end_time": 43396.0,
      "text": "like there&#39;s a man,"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 43396.0,
      "end_time": 45137.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s walking down the sidewalk,"
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 45137.0,
      "end_time": 48273.0,
      "text": "without realizing it, he crosses over an open manhole,"
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 48273.0,
      "end_time": 51958.0,
      "text": "and he just plummets into the sewer below."
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51958.0,
      "end_time": 56769.0,
      "text": "And I picture it this way because falling is not jumping."
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 56769.0,
      "end_time": 58825.0,
      "text": "Falling is accidental,"
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 58825.0,
      "end_time": 60751.0,
      "text": "it&#39;s uncontrollable."
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 60751.0,
      "end_time": 64300.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s something that happens to us without our consent."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 64300.0,
      "end_time": 65517.0,
      "text": "And this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65516.99999999999,
      "end_time": 70336.0,
      "text": "this is the main way we talk about starting a new relationship."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 70336.0,
      "end_time": 74127.0,
      "text": "I am a writer and I&#39;m also an English teacher,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 74127.0,
      "end_time": 76436.0,
      "text": "which means I think about words for a living."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 76436.0,
      "end_time": 80610.0,
      "text": "You could say that I get paid to argue that the language we use matters,"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 80610.0,
      "end_time": 84834.0,
      "text": "and I would like to argue that many of the metaphors we use"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 84834.0,
      "end_time": 86425.0,
      "text": "to talk about love --"
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 86425.0,
      "end_time": 88272.0,
      "text": "maybe even most of them --"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 88272.0,
      "end_time": 90700.0,
      "text": "are a problem."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 90700.0,
      "end_time": 93766.0,
      "text": "So, in love, we fall."
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 93766.0,
      "end_time": 95255.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re struck."
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 95255.0,
      "end_time": 97331.0,
      "text": "We are crushed."
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 97331.0,
      "end_time": 99186.0,
      "text": "We swoon."
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 99186.0,
      "end_time": 101738.0,
      "text": "We burn with passion."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 101738.0,
      "end_time": 103739.0,
      "text": "Love makes us crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 103739.0,
      "end_time": 105796.0,
      "text": "and it makes us sick."
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 105796.0,
      "end_time": 107180.0,
      "text": "Our hearts ache,"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 107180.0,
      "end_time": 110226.0,
      "text": "and then they break."
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 110226.0,
      "end_time": 113394.0,
      "text": "So our metaphors equate the experience of loving someone"
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 113394.0,
      "end_time": 116071.0,
      "text": "to extreme violence or illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 116071.0,
      "end_time": 119101.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 119101.0,
      "end_time": 120276.0,
      "text": "They do."
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 120276.0,
      "end_time": 122283.0,
      "text": "And they position us as the victims"
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 122283.0,
      "end_time": 126547.0,
      "text": "of unforeseen and totally unavoidable circumstances."
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 126547.0,
      "end_time": 129294.0,
      "text": "My favorite one of these is &quot;smitten,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 129294.00000000001,
      "end_time": 132172.0,
      "text": "which is the past participle of the word &quot;smite.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 132172.0,
      "end_time": 135264.0,
      "text": "And if you look this word up in the dictionary --"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 135264.0,
      "end_time": 136312.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 136312.0,
      "end_time": 140854.0,
      "text": "you will see that it can be defined as both &quot;grievous affliction,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 140854.0,
      "end_time": 145716.0,
      "text": "and, &quot;to be very much in love.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 145716.0,
      "end_time": 149084.0,
      "text": "I tend to associate the word &quot;smite&quot; with a very particular context,"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 149084.0,
      "end_time": 151560.0,
      "text": "which is the Old Testament."
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 151560.0,
      "end_time": 156332.0,
      "text": "In the Book of Exodus alone, there are 16 references to smiting,"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 156332.0,
      "end_time": 160129.0,
      "text": "which is the word that the Bible uses for the vengeance of an angry God."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 160129.0,
      "end_time": 161874.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 161874.0,
      "end_time": 164603.0,
      "text": "Here we are using the same word to talk about love"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 164603.0,
      "end_time": 167053.0,
      "text": "that we use to explain a plague of locusts."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 167053.0,
      "end_time": 168105.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 168105.0,
      "end_time": 169385.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 169385.0,
      "end_time": 171501.0,
      "text": "So, how did this happen?"
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 171501.0,
      "end_time": 175516.0,
      "text": "How have we come to associate love with great pain and suffering?"
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 175516.0,
      "end_time": 179529.0,
      "text": "And why do we talk about this ostensibly good experience"
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 179529.0,
      "end_time": 182556.0,
      "text": "as if we are victims?"
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 182556.0,
      "end_time": 184271.0,
      "text": "These are difficult questions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 184271.0,
      "end_time": 185941.0,
      "text": "but I have some theories."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 185941.0,
      "end_time": 187204.0,
      "text": "And to think this through,"
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 187204.0,
      "end_time": 189856.0,
      "text": "I want to focus on one metaphor in particular,"
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 189856.0,
      "end_time": 193088.0,
      "text": "which is the idea of love as madness."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 193088.0,
      "end_time": 195819.0,
      "text": "When I first started researching romantic love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 195819.0,
      "end_time": 198604.0,
      "text": "I found these madness metaphors everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 198604.0,
      "end_time": 200731.0,
      "text": "The history of Western culture"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 200731.0,
      "end_time": 205440.0,
      "text": "is full of language that equates love to mental illness."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 205440.0,
      "end_time": 207391.0,
      "text": "These are just a few examples."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 207391.0,
      "end_time": 208758.0,
      "text": "William Shakespeare:"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 208758.0,
      "end_time": 210215.0,
      "text": "&quot;Love is merely a madness,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 210215.0,
      "end_time": 212092.0,
      "text": "from &quot;As You Like It.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 212092.0,
      "end_time": 213373.0,
      "text": "Friedrich Nietzsche:"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 213373.0,
      "end_time": 216559.0,
      "text": "&quot;There is always some madness in love.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 216559.0,
      "end_time": 219449.0,
      "text": "&quot;Got me looking, got me looking so crazy in love -- &quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 219449.0,
      "end_time": 221542.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 221542.0,
      "end_time": 224164.0,
      "text": "from the great philosopher, Beyoncé Knowles."
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 224164.0,
      "end_time": 227083.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 227083.0,
      "end_time": 229941.0,
      "text": "I fell in love for the first time when I was 20,"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 229941.0,
      "end_time": 233459.0,
      "text": "and it was a pretty turbulent relationship right from the start."
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 233459.0,
      "end_time": 236688.0,
      "text": "And it was long distance for the first couple of years,"
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 236688.0,
      "end_time": 241794.0,
      "text": "so for me that meant very high highs and very low lows."
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 241794.0,
      "end_time": 244580.0,
      "text": "I can remember one moment in particular."
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 244580.0,
      "end_time": 247949.0,
      "text": "I was sitting on a bed in a hostel in South America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 247949.0,
      "end_time": 252151.0,
      "text": "and I was watching the person I love walk out the door."
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 252151.0,
      "end_time": 253788.0,
      "text": "And it was late,"
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 253788.0,
      "end_time": 255072.0,
      "text": "it was nearly midnight,"
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 255072.0,
      "end_time": 257073.0,
      "text": "we&#39;d gotten into an argument over dinner,"
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 257072.99999999997,
      "end_time": 259045.99999999997,
      "text": "and when we got back to our room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 259046.0,
      "end_time": 263141.0,
      "text": "he threw his things in the bag and stormed out."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 263141.0,
      "end_time": 266424.0,
      "text": "While I can no longer remember what that argument was about,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 266424.0,
      "end_time": 271122.0,
      "text": "I very clearly remember how I felt watching him leave."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 271122.0,
      "end_time": 275424.0,
      "text": "I was 22, it was my first time in the developing world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 275424.0,
      "end_time": 278412.0,
      "text": "and I was totally alone."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 278412.0,
      "end_time": 281803.0,
      "text": "I had another week until my flight home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 281803.0,
      "end_time": 284195.0,
      "text": "and I knew the name of the town that I was in,"
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 284195.0,
      "end_time": 287802.0,
      "text": "and the name of the city that I needed to get to to fly out,"
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 287802.0,
      "end_time": 291842.0,
      "text": "but I had no idea how to get around."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 291842.0,
      "end_time": 295043.0,
      "text": "I had no guidebook and very little money,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 295043.0,
      "end_time": 297547.0,
      "text": "and I spoke no Spanish."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 297547.0,
      "end_time": 299668.0,
      "text": "Someone more adventurous than me"
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 299668.0,
      "end_time": 302122.0,
      "text": "might have seen this as a moment of opportunity,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 302122.0,
      "end_time": 304406.0,
      "text": "but I just froze."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 304406.0,
      "end_time": 306738.0,
      "text": "I just sat there."
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 306738.0,
      "end_time": 309357.0,
      "text": "And then I burst into tears."
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 309357.0,
      "end_time": 311752.0,
      "text": "But despite my panic,"
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 311752.0,
      "end_time": 314346.0,
      "text": "some small voice in my head thought,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 314346.0,
      "end_time": 316707.0,
      "text": "&quot;Wow. That was dramatic."
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 316707.0,
      "end_time": 319430.0,
      "text": "I must really be doing this love thing right.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 319430.0,
      "end_time": 321242.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 321242.0,
      "end_time": 326226.0,
      "text": "Because some part of me wanted to feel miserable in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 326226.0,
      "end_time": 329690.0,
      "text": "And it sounds so strange to me now, but at 22,"
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 329690.0,
      "end_time": 332859.0,
      "text": "I longed to have dramatic experiences,"
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 332859.0,
      "end_time": 338081.0,
      "text": "and in that moment, I was irrational and furious and devastated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 338081.0,
      "end_time": 339329.0,
      "text": "and weirdly enough,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 339329.0,
      "end_time": 342729.0,
      "text": "I thought that this somehow legitimized the feelings I had"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 342729.0,
      "end_time": 346163.0,
      "text": "for the guy who had just left me."
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 346163.0,
      "end_time": 350550.0,
      "text": "I think on some level I wanted to feel a little bit crazy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 350550.0,
      "end_time": 355141.0,
      "text": "because I thought that that was how loved worked."
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 355141.0,
      "end_time": 356972.0,
      "text": "This really should not be surprising,"
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 356972.0,
      "end_time": 359450.0,
      "text": "considering that according to Wikipedia,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 359450.0,
      "end_time": 361747.0,
      "text": "there are eight films,"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 361747.0,
      "end_time": 363768.0,
      "text": "14 songs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 363768.0,
      "end_time": 367837.0,
      "text": "two albums and one novel with the title &quot;Crazy Love.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 367837.0,
      "end_time": 370987.0,
      "text": "About half an hour later, he came back to our room."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 370987.0,
      "end_time": 372162.0,
      "text": "We made up."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 372162.0,
      "end_time": 375003.0,
      "text": "We spent another mostly happy week traveling together."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 375003.0,
      "end_time": 376459.0,
      "text": "And then, when I got home,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 376459.0,
      "end_time": 381989.0,
      "text": "I thought, &quot;That was so terrible and so great."
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 381989.0,
      "end_time": 385006.0,
      "text": "This must be a real romance.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 385006.0,
      "end_time": 387730.0,
      "text": "I expected my first love to feel like madness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 387730.0,
      "end_time": 391941.0,
      "text": "and of course, it met that expectation very well."
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 391941.0,
      "end_time": 393656.0,
      "text": "But loving someone like that --"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 393656.0,
      "end_time": 397775.0,
      "text": "as if my entire well-being depended on him loving me back --"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 397775.0,
      "end_time": 399892.0,
      "text": "was not very good for me"
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 399892.0,
      "end_time": 401850.0,
      "text": "or for him."
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 401850.0,
      "end_time": 406026.0,
      "text": "But I suspect this experience of love is not that unusual."
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 406026.0,
      "end_time": 410815.0,
      "text": "Most of us do feel a bit mad in the early stages of romantic love."
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 410815.0,
      "end_time": 415280.0,
      "text": "In fact, there is research to confirm that this is somewhat normal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 415280.0,
      "end_time": 417190.0,
      "text": "because, neurochemically speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 417190.0,
      "end_time": 423046.0,
      "text": "romantic love and mental illness are not that easily distinguished."
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 423046.0,
      "end_time": 424221.0,
      "text": "This is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 424221.0,
      "end_time": 428804.0,
      "text": "This study from 1999 used blood tests"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 428804.0,
      "end_time": 431922.0,
      "text": "to confirm that the serotonin levels of the newly in love"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 431922.0,
      "end_time": 434743.0,
      "text": "very closely resembled the serotonin levels"
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 434743.0,
      "end_time": 438072.0,
      "text": "of people who had been diagnosed with obsessive-compulsive disorder."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 438072.0,
      "end_time": 439104.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 439104.0,
      "end_time": 441825.0,
      "text": "Yes, and low levels of serotonin"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 441825.0,
      "end_time": 445451.0,
      "text": "are also associated with seasonal affective disorder"
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 445451.0,
      "end_time": 447687.0,
      "text": "and depression."
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 447687.0,
      "end_time": 449971.0,
      "text": "So there is some evidence"
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 449971.0,
      "end_time": 454343.0,
      "text": "that love is associated with changes to our moods and our behaviors."
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 454343.0,
      "end_time": 458374.0,
      "text": "And there are other studies to confirm"
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 458374.0,
      "end_time": 462660.0,
      "text": "that most relationships begin this way."
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 462660.0,
      "end_time": 466847.0,
      "text": "Researchers believe that the low levels of serotonin"
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 466847.0,
      "end_time": 470906.0,
      "text": "is correlated with obsessive thinking about the object of love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 470906.0,
      "end_time": 474988.0,
      "text": "which is like this feeling that someone has set up camp in your brain."
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 474988.0,
      "end_time": 477943.0,
      "text": "And most of us feel this way when we first fall in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 477943.0,
      "end_time": 481093.0,
      "text": "But the good news is, it doesn&#39;t always last that long --"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 481093.0,
      "end_time": 485352.0,
      "text": "usually from a few months to a couple of years."
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 485352.0,
      "end_time": 488184.0,
      "text": "When I got back from my trip to South America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 488184.0,
      "end_time": 491785.0,
      "text": "I spent a lot of time alone in my room,"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 491785.0,
      "end_time": 493149.0,
      "text": "checking my email,"
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 493149.0,
      "end_time": 496545.0,
      "text": "desperate to hear from the guy I loved."
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 496545.0,
      "end_time": 501917.0,
      "text": "I decided that if my friends could not understand my grievous affliction,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 501917.0,
      "end_time": 503890.0,
      "text": "then I did not need their friendship."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 503890.0,
      "end_time": 506387.0,
      "text": "So I stopped hanging out with most of them."
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 506387.0,
      "end_time": 511086.0,
      "text": "And it was probably the most unhappy year of my life."
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 511086.0,
      "end_time": 515849.0,
      "text": "But I think I felt like it was my job to be miserable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 515849.00000000006,
      "end_time": 517665.00000000006,
      "text": "because if I could be miserable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 517664.99999999994,
      "end_time": 520355.99999999994,
      "text": "then I would prove how much I loved him."
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 520356.0,
      "end_time": 522265.0,
      "text": "And if I could prove it,"
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 522265.0,
      "end_time": 526050.0,
      "text": "then we would have to end up together eventually."
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 526050.0,
      "end_time": 528162.0,
      "text": "This is the real madness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 528162.0,
      "end_time": 530581.0,
      "text": "because there is no cosmic rule"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 530581.0,
      "end_time": 534478.0,
      "text": "that says that great suffering equals great reward,"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 534478.0,
      "end_time": 539463.0,
      "text": "but we talk about love as if this is true."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 539463.0,
      "end_time": 543774.0,
      "text": "Our experiences of love are both biological and cultural."
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 543774.0,
      "end_time": 546257.0,
      "text": "Our biology tells us that love is good"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 546257.0,
      "end_time": 549435.0,
      "text": "by activating these reward circuits in our brain,"
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 549435.0,
      "end_time": 554079.0,
      "text": "and it tells us that love is painful when, after a fight or a breakup,"
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 554079.0,
      "end_time": 557155.0,
      "text": "that neurochemical reward is withdrawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 557155.0,
      "end_time": 559621.0,
      "text": "And in fact -- and maybe you&#39;ve heard this --"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 559621.0,
      "end_time": 561489.0,
      "text": "neurochemically speaking,"
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 561489.0,
      "end_time": 565675.0,
      "text": "going through a breakup is a lot like going through cocaine withdrawal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 565675.0,
      "end_time": 567335.0,
      "text": "which I find reassuring."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 567335.0,
      "end_time": 569066.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 569066.0,
      "end_time": 571922.0,
      "text": "And then our culture uses language"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 571922.0,
      "end_time": 574727.0,
      "text": "to shape and reinforce these ideas about love."
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 574727.0,
      "end_time": 577375.0,
      "text": "In this case, we&#39;re talking about metaphors about pain"
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 577375.0,
      "end_time": 579826.0,
      "text": "and addiction and madness."
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 579826.0,
      "end_time": 582294.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s kind of an interesting feedback loop."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 582294.0,
      "end_time": 585835.0,
      "text": "Love is powerful and at times painful,"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 585835.0,
      "end_time": 589182.0,
      "text": "and we express this in our words and stories,"
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 589182.0,
      "end_time": 591704.0,
      "text": "but then our words and stories prime us"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 591704.0,
      "end_time": 595955.0,
      "text": "to expect love to be powerful and painful."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 595955.0,
      "end_time": 599152.0,
      "text": "What&#39;s interesting to me is that all of this happens"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 599152.0,
      "end_time": 602658.0,
      "text": "in a culture that values lifelong monogamy."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 602658.0,
      "end_time": 604743.0,
      "text": "It seems like we want it both ways:"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 604743.0,
      "end_time": 607718.0,
      "text": "we want love to feel like madness,"
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 607718.0,
      "end_time": 611561.0,
      "text": "and we want it to last an entire lifetime."
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 611561.0,
      "end_time": 613148.0,
      "text": "That sounds terrible."
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 613148.0,
      "end_time": 615853.0,
      "text": "(Laughter)"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 615853.0,
      "end_time": 617473.0,
      "text": "To reconcile this,"
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 617473.0,
      "end_time": 623408.0,
      "text": "we need to either change our culture or change our expectations."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 623408.0,
      "end_time": 627642.0,
      "text": "So, imagine if we were all less passive in love."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 627642.0,
      "end_time": 631812.0,
      "text": "If we were more assertive, more open-minded, more generous"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 631812.0,
      "end_time": 635137.0,
      "text": "and instead of falling in love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 635137.0,
      "end_time": 638223.0,
      "text": "we stepped into love."
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 638223.0,
      "end_time": 640176.0,
      "text": "I know that this is asking a lot,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 640176.0,
      "end_time": 645012.0,
      "text": "but I&#39;m not actually the first person to suggest this."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 645012.0,
      "end_time": 647545.0,
      "text": "In their book, &quot;Metaphors We Live By,&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 647545.0,
      "end_time": 652683.0,
      "text": "linguists Mark Johnson and George Lakoff suggest a really interesting solution"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 652683.0,
      "end_time": 654491.0,
      "text": "to this dilemma,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 654491.0,
      "end_time": 657795.0,
      "text": "which is to change our metaphors."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 657795.0,
      "end_time": 663071.0,
      "text": "They argue that metaphors really do shape the way we experience the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 663071.0,
      "end_time": 666593.0,
      "text": "and that they can even act as a guide for future actions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 666593.0,
      "end_time": 669489.0,
      "text": "like self-fulfilling prophecies."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 669489.0,
      "end_time": 673977.0,
      "text": "Johnson and Lakoff suggest a new metaphor for love:"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 673977.0,
      "end_time": 676872.0,
      "text": "love as a collaborative work of art."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 676872.0,
      "end_time": 681028.0,
      "text": "I really like this way of thinking about love."
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 681028.0,
      "end_time": 684574.0,
      "text": "Linguists talk about metaphors as having entailments,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 684574.0,
      "end_time": 688394.0,
      "text": "which is essentially a way of considering all the implications of,"
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 688394.0,
      "end_time": 691350.0,
      "text": "or ideas contained within, a given metaphor."
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 691350.0,
      "end_time": 694283.0,
      "text": "And Johnson and Lakoff talk about everything"
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 694283.0,
      "end_time": 696976.0,
      "text": "that collaborating on a work of art entails:"
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 696976.0,
      "end_time": 701655.0,
      "text": "effort, compromise, patience, shared goals."
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 701655.0,
      "end_time": 705509.0,
      "text": "These ideas align nicely with our cultural investment"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 705509.0,
      "end_time": 707606.0,
      "text": "in long-term romantic commitment,"
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 707606.0,
      "end_time": 712020.0,
      "text": "but they also work well for other kinds of relationships --"
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 712020.0,
      "end_time": 717700.0,
      "text": "short-term, casual, polyamorous, non-monogamous, asexual --"
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 717700.0,
      "end_time": 721609.0,
      "text": "because this metaphor brings much more complex ideas"
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 721609.0,
      "end_time": 724670.0,
      "text": "to the experience of loving someone."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 724670.0,
      "end_time": 729088.0,
      "text": "So if love is a collaborative work of art,"
    },
    {
      "index": 237,
      "start_time": 729088.0,
      "end_time": 733524.0,
      "text": "then love is an aesthetic experience."
    },
    {
      "index": 238,
      "start_time": 733524.0,
      "end_time": 736153.0,
      "text": "Love is unpredictable,"
    },
    {
      "index": 239,
      "start_time": 736153.0,
      "end_time": 738898.0,
      "text": "love is creative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 240,
      "start_time": 738898.0,
      "end_time": 743055.0,
      "text": "love requires communication and discipline,"
    },
    {
      "index": 241,
      "start_time": 743055.0,
      "end_time": 746677.0,
      "text": "it is frustrating and emotionally demanding."
    },
    {
      "index": 242,
      "start_time": 746677.0,
      "end_time": 750742.0,
      "text": "And love involves both joy and pain."
    },
    {
      "index": 243,
      "start_time": 750742.0,
      "end_time": 755759.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, each experience of love is different."
    },
    {
      "index": 244,
      "start_time": 755759.0,
      "end_time": 757410.0,
      "text": "When I was younger,"
    },
    {
      "index": 245,
      "start_time": 757410.0,
      "end_time": 762102.0,
      "text": "it never occurred to me that I was allowed to demand more from love,"
    },
    {
      "index": 246,
      "start_time": 762102.0,
      "end_time": 766775.0,
      "text": "that I didn&#39;t have to just accept whatever love offered."
    },
    {
      "index": 247,
      "start_time": 766775.0,
      "end_time": 770128.0,
      "text": "When 14-year-old Juliet first meets --"
    },
    {
      "index": 248,
      "start_time": 770128.0,
      "end_time": 774077.0,
      "text": "or, when 14-year-old Juliet cannot be with Romeo,"
    },
    {
      "index": 249,
      "start_time": 774077.0,
      "end_time": 776738.0,
      "text": "whom she has met four days ago,"
    },
    {
      "index": 250,
      "start_time": 776738.0,
      "end_time": 781022.0,
      "text": "she does not feel disappointed or angsty."
    },
    {
      "index": 251,
      "start_time": 781022.0,
      "end_time": 782403.0,
      "text": "Where is she?"
    },
    {
      "index": 252,
      "start_time": 782403.0,
      "end_time": 784236.0,
      "text": "She wants to die."
    },
    {
      "index": 253,
      "start_time": 784236.0,
      "end_time": 785411.0,
      "text": "Right?"
    },
    {
      "index": 254,
      "start_time": 785411.0,
      "end_time": 787904.0,
      "text": "And just as a refresher, at this point in the play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 255,
      "start_time": 787904.0,
      "end_time": 789236.0,
      "text": "act three of five,"
    },
    {
      "index": 256,
      "start_time": 789236.0,
      "end_time": 791641.0,
      "text": "Romeo is not dead."
    },
    {
      "index": 257,
      "start_time": 791641.0,
      "end_time": 793005.0,
      "text": "He&#39;s alive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 258,
      "start_time": 793005.0,
      "end_time": 794417.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s healthy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 259,
      "start_time": 794417.0,
      "end_time": 797853.0,
      "text": "he&#39;s just been banished from the city."
    },
    {
      "index": 260,
      "start_time": 797853.0,
      "end_time": 803878.0,
      "text": "I understand that 16th-century Verona is unlike contemporary North America,"
    },
    {
      "index": 261,
      "start_time": 803878.0,
      "end_time": 806880.0,
      "text": "and yet when I first read this play,"
    },
    {
      "index": 262,
      "start_time": 806880.0,
      "end_time": 809297.0,
      "text": "also at age 14,"
    },
    {
      "index": 263,
      "start_time": 809297.0,
      "end_time": 813295.0,
      "text": "Juliet&#39;s suffering made sense to me."
    },
    {
      "index": 264,
      "start_time": 813295.0,
      "end_time": 818676.0,
      "text": "Reframing love as something I get to create with someone I admire,"
    },
    {
      "index": 265,
      "start_time": 818676.0,
      "end_time": 821144.0,
      "text": "rather than something that just happens to me"
    },
    {
      "index": 266,
      "start_time": 821144.0,
      "end_time": 823690.0,
      "text": "without my control or consent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 267,
      "start_time": 823690.0,
      "end_time": 825779.0,
      "text": "is empowering."
    },
    {
      "index": 268,
      "start_time": 825779.0,
      "end_time": 827421.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s still hard."
    },
    {
      "index": 269,
      "start_time": 827421.0,
      "end_time": 832977.0,
      "text": "Love still feels totally maddening and crushing some days,"
    },
    {
      "index": 270,
      "start_time": 832977.0,
      "end_time": 835116.0,
      "text": "and when I feel really frustrated,"
    },
    {
      "index": 271,
      "start_time": 835116.0,
      "end_time": 836995.0,
      "text": "I have to remind myself:"
    },
    {
      "index": 272,
      "start_time": 836995.0,
      "end_time": 840363.0,
      "text": "my job in this relationship is to talk to my partner"
    },
    {
      "index": 273,
      "start_time": 840363.0,
      "end_time": 843923.0,
      "text": "about what I want to make together."
    },
    {
      "index": 274,
      "start_time": 843923.0,
      "end_time": 846756.0,
      "text": "This isn&#39;t easy, either."
    },
    {
      "index": 275,
      "start_time": 846756.0,
      "end_time": 850672.0,
      "text": "But it&#39;s just so much better than the alternative,"
    },
    {
      "index": 276,
      "start_time": 850672.0,
      "end_time": 854839.0,
      "text": "which is that thing that feels like madness."
    },
    {
      "index": 277,
      "start_time": 854839.0,
      "end_time": 860761.0,
      "text": "This version of love is not about winning or losing someone&#39;s affection."
    },
    {
      "index": 278,
      "start_time": 860761.0,
      "end_time": 864383.0,
      "text": "Instead, it requires that you trust your partner"
    },
    {
      "index": 279,
      "start_time": 864383.0,
      "end_time": 867481.0,
      "text": "and talk about things when trusting feels difficult,"
    },
    {
      "index": 280,
      "start_time": 867481.0,
      "end_time": 869951.0,
      "text": "which sounds so simple,"
    },
    {
      "index": 281,
      "start_time": 869951.0,
      "end_time": 875062.0,
      "text": "but is actually a kind of revolutionary, radical act."
    },
    {
      "index": 282,
      "start_time": 875062.0,
      "end_time": 879230.0,
      "text": "This is because you get to stop thinking about yourself"
    },
    {
      "index": 283,
      "start_time": 879230.0,
      "end_time": 882395.0,
      "text": "and what you&#39;re gaining or losing in your relationship,"
    },
    {
      "index": 284,
      "start_time": 882395.0,
      "end_time": 886811.0,
      "text": "and you get to start thinking about what you have to offer."
    },
    {
      "index": 285,
      "start_time": 886811.0,
      "end_time": 890240.0,
      "text": "This version of love allows us to say things like,"
    },
    {
      "index": 286,
      "start_time": 890240.0,
      "end_time": 895733.0,
      "text": "&quot;Hey, we&#39;re not very good collaborators. Maybe this isn&#39;t for us.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 287,
      "start_time": 895733.0,
      "end_time": 899618.0,
      "text": "Or, &quot;That relationship was shorter than I had planned,"
    },
    {
      "index": 288,
      "start_time": 899618.0,
      "end_time": 902836.0,
      "text": "but it was still kind of beautiful.&quot;"
    },
    {
      "index": 289,
      "start_time": 902836.0,
      "end_time": 905650.0,
      "text": "The beautiful thing about the collaborative work of art"
    },
    {
      "index": 290,
      "start_time": 905650.0,
      "end_time": 909098.0,
      "text": "is that it will not paint or draw or sculpt itself."
    },
    {
      "index": 291,
      "start_time": 909098.0,
      "end_time": 913033.0,
      "text": "This version of love allows us to decide what it looks like."
    },
    {
      "index": 292,
      "start_time": 913033.0,
      "end_time": 914208.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 293,
      "start_time": 914208.0,
      "end_time": 924208.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}